text: Average players might now become great in sports, current champions may have to double their training.
Thieves will have their task cut out, they may get caught red-handed every single time.
Villains may now have the upper-hand, superheroes might start hiding from them.
Ophthalmologists i.e. people who specialize in treating eye related problems may double their fees.
Fifthly, if we had 4 Eyes, some people may take multitasking to a different level altogether.
Lastly, Pirates are known to wear a patch over one eye.
If we had 4 Eyes, they may have to order more patches.
